    General Stores in Cotton Green, Mumbai

    (233 Ratings & Reviews) 4.1 Average Ratings

    General Stores in Cotton Green, Mumbai

    Commonly known as 'kiranas' in the local parlance, mom-n-pop shops are nothing but general stores. It is a form of traditional retail where it offers a wide range of products. In certain metros and cities, a general store can also be a part of a pharmacy or medicine shop. Any of these stores house a vast variety of products ranging from loose grains and pulses to cosmetics. General store products comprise of food grains, pulses, household items, toiletries, cosmetics, biscuits and packaged food items, bakery products, confectionery items, and local foods. Catering to the convenience of their customers, these shops also extend free home delivery service. These store owners work in conjunction with wholesalers, distributors, and retailers forming a wide network in the city or town. Mentioned above is a vast list of General Stores in Cotton Green, Mumbai.
